st like yours  companies financed as a team   average revenue growth by merion companies  years of experience testimonials here’s what just some of our clients have said merion supported id images with capital strategic advice and sourcing potential acquisition opportunities everyone talks about being a partner but few live the true meaning of the term merion is a true partner brian gale — id images ceo t brian gale — id images ceo merion supported id images with capital strategic advice and sourcing potential acquisition opportunities everyone talks about being a partner but few live the true meaning of the term merion is a true partner httpwwwmerionpartnerscomtestimonials when afs started on its strategy to grow through acquisitions the company had no track record of historical earnings but based on the management vision merion was the only one that understood the value proposition and provided the capital needed at a critical time for afs their support of management in continuing the growth strategy by providing additional funding and counsel when needed resulted in afs being one of the most successful software company rollups of the last decade and merion was a pivotal part of that success kurien jacob — anju software inc ceo t kurien jacob — anju software inc ceo when afs started on its strategy to grow through acquisitions the company had no track record of historical earnings but based on the management vision merion was the only one that understood the value proposition and provided the capital needed at a critical time for afs their support of management in continuing the growth strategy view full → httpwwwmerionpartnerscomtestimonialskurienjacobanjusoftwareincceo merion is responsive and decisive with merion’s assistance we closed two add on acquisitions for our platform in a very timely and seamless fashion their speed professionalism and willingness to pose solutions helped our company to grow both organically and through consolidation of competitors and